text:
Vojtěch Mynář (4 May 1944 – 11 July 2018) was a Czech politician. From 2012 until 2014, he was a Member of the European Parliament, representing the Czech Republic. He was a member of the Social Democratic Party. Mynář was born in Petřvald, Czechoslovakia.
Mynář died on 11 July 2018 in Prague at the age of 74.
